page.title: 08A TYPICAL SUNDAY,CONNEL
page.content: I wake up around 0730 and read until 0900.Then I have my breakfast.After it I go to the service in the Roman Catholic Church of St.Louis and St Margaret at 1000.It finishes at 1030.I walk home with my parents and my sister.When I get home I have a snack then go for a ride on my bike.Sometimes I play a game with some others.I then have my dinner After it I play until tea at 1715.I go back out to play until 2000.I then go in and have my hair washed.I have my supper and read until bedtme which is around 2200.My sister who is 13 goes to bed before me.
